<html>
  <head>
    <title>log-hmm</title>
    <link href="./meme-suite.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="main">
      <script src="./meme-suite-logo.js" type="text/javascript">></script>
      <h1>log-hmm</h1>

      <p>
        <b>Usage:</b> <code>log-hmm [options] &lt;<i>HMM file</i>&gt;</code>
      </p>

      <p><b>Description:</b></p>
      <p>
        This program converts a HMM file generated by 
        <code><a href="miao.html">mhmm</a></code> or 
        <code><a href="beadstring.html">Beadstring</a></code>
        from probabilites to log probabilities.
      </p>

      <p><b>Input:</b></p>

      <ul>
      <li>&lt;<i>HMM file</i>&gt; - a file containing the description of a HMM in
      <a href="mhmm-output.html">mhmm format</a>.</li>
      </ul>

      <p><b>Output:</b></p>
      <p>
      The program prints to standard output the same HMM but with
      log probabilities rather then probabilities.
      </p>

      <p><b>Options:</b></p>

      <ul>
      <li><command-option name="verbosity"/></li>
      </ul>

      <p><b>Bugs:</b> None known.</p>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>
